# Commitlint
From: https://github.com/conventional-changelog/commitlint
* Common types according to commitlint-config-conventional can be:
- build
- chore
- ci
- docs
- feat
- fix
- perf
- refactor
- revert
- style
- test
These can be modified by your own configuration.

